Class CartItem

java.lang.Object
app.CartItem
public class CartItem extends Object
Represents an item being added to the cart including different drink, topping, and customization options.

    • CartItem

      public CartItem(Drink drink, Topping topping, String size, String iceLevel, String sweetness, double price, int quantity)
      Creates a new CartItem containing a drink and its selected options.
      Parameters:
      drink - the drink ordered
      topping - the topping added, or null if none
      size - drink size selection
      iceLevel - ice customization level
      sweetness - selected sweetness level
      price - price of a single drink with selected options
      quantity - number of units of this item ordered
